{"tid":2269092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被捕 何君堯：「自設陷阱」","createTime":"2020-11-03T09:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:30:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd6c9397b507a4da220a0bce6c7b0ba8d70c2e3","tid":2269092,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）有份參與製作《鏗鏘集：7.21誰主真相》節目的香港電台電視部編導蔡玉玲，今日被警方拘捕，指以不正當資料做車輛查冊，涉嫌違反《道路交通條例》。立法會議員何君堯被記者問到是否與元朗721事件有關，「千奇唔好cheat、唔好呃，唔好作虛假聲明（就無事）。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯指並不清楚案件詳情，又稱支持記者探求事實、為公眾服務，並指自己對第四公權揭露真相「予以肯定」，但強調傳媒在尋找真相的過程中不可有「鋌而走險」、「踩界」的成分，「法律始終要去遵守」。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，傳媒填寫表格要小心，一旦提供錯誤訊息便等同作虛假聲明，後果可大可小，又建議記者若不清楚可徵詢律師意見，以避免不必要後果，不斷重複「小心啲做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到過往不少記者均以查冊方式獲取所需資料，但今次卻被指「踩界」，是否具政治目的針對港台。他回應指，「索取公開檔案嘅應用係乜要講真說話，如實講真說話就無問題。」他更指過往沒有後果不代表做法恰當，「勿以惡少以為之」、「係咪撥亂反正呀，我唔知。」<br />\n<br />\n記者再追問是次拘捕是否與721事件有關，何君堯再指現時不清楚詳情，僅強調「千奇唔好cheat、唔好呃，唔好作虛假聲明」，又指蔡玉玲作虛假聲明的「陷阱」很明顯，「自己set咗自己落去」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078592&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=3eb0b647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078592&h=2a285c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078592</a>"},{"pid":"2fe0e9a9640d3e4ef75410b9765cf1b5db2f46c8","tid":2269092,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950ccaa5a85272f4bd2487b7d39f7b819446888b","tid":2269092,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5c49fb863734a74f958b2e4a0a6bfbe6648dfb","tid":2269092,"uid":297609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"咁係唔係要市民比錢自己做查冊？ 事實又點樣虛假聲明？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以言人罪"},{"pid":"f8220aab2924f9c258d30fe2c3f4440cd9000ae4","tid":2269092,"uid":146556,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHMMGip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHMMGip.jpg&h=337b56ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自設陷阱"},{"pid":"9b14fa75f71a2393a0f593aaab8fcf0d03fee6ae","tid":2269092,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"親港共武裝恐怖份子想改寫香港人記憶呀~~<br />\n<br />\n第一步就係貶低記者消息來源可信性....<br />\n推論落去就係消息來源唔可信...<br />\n所以成個製作就令人懷疑...<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦~~ 親港共武裝恐怖份子~~ 你地做咩都唔會令人唔再憎你地架啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195c90f1f581ecc898c59e7b43af2152b1ed12e1","tid":2269092,"uid":225291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"不正當資料做車輛查冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「車輛登記細節證明書」的申請應用作以下用途：<br />\n進行與運輸相關的法律程序<br />\n買賣車輛<br />\n有關交通及運輸的事宜</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新聞報道唔得, 拉!"},{"pid":"834c59feed711335be69531448f861035557011d","tid":2269092,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"何妖做咩咁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d2da2d286d64bdd4a71cf4e989fa093f73d91c","tid":2269092,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8220aab2924f9c258d30fe2c3f4440cd9000ae4","tid":2269092,"uid":146556,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHMMGip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht